“You do not understand,” he said at length. “Mrs. Hall is a very well-known society lady and has numerous connections in official circles. Thank God we live in a great country, where everybody can speak his mind without being insulted for expressing a private opinion.”

I told him to go away.

When my final splutter had petered out, he said, “I go away, but please remember, in this country—” and he shook his bent finger at me sidew